# GoalifyNow.Api

## Scope

`backend/GoalifyNow.Api` — ASP.NET Core / FastEndpoints API (.NET 10), EF Core, migrations via root `pnpm` scripts.

## Practices

- Follow FastEndpoints patterns already present: endpoints, validators, and OpenAPI metadata via `Summary()` and `[Description]` where the project uses them
- Prefer clear request/response records per endpoint to avoid validator discovery collisions
- Keep EF Core queries filterable in the database; avoid client-side filtering of large sets
- Use Shouldly in tests if test projects exist; do not introduce FluentAssertions
- After schema changes, use `pnpm db:migration:add` / `pnpm db:migrate` as appropriate, then verify builds
